13. What is the impact of COVID-19 on the smart moisture sensors market?
The COVID-19 pandemic has led to disruptions in the supply chain and decreased investment in the agriculture and construction sectors, affecting the demand for smart moisture sensors.

14. What are the future growth prospects for the smart moisture sensors market?
The future growth prospects for the smart moisture sensors market are promising, driven by increasing adoption of precision agriculture practices and advancements in sensor technology.

